{"tid":1881612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實醫護好慘，請大家正視工會問題","createTime":"2020-02-15T16:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T18:34:45.000Z","uid":251736,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"43fbe9043063830f53c8bdd6ddbff758030cfa1c","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我好尊敬有罷工嘅醫護，但同時希望工會改善下</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌你老母垃圾工會</span><br />\n<br />\n好多醫護都知道醫護罷工係道德兩難，一方面要政府封關，一方面唔想影響病人，但係最後大家都選擇罷工，係人都知罷工係放病人上抬威脅政府，係有民意基礎而且係人都知政府on9嘅時候，根本唔會民意逆轉。換這之，罷工係一個鬥痴線遊戲，為左封關而唔理非緊急病人係痴線，政府唔封關都係痴線。<br />\n<br />\n以上對罷工的理解肯定所有有罷工的同事都知道。如果政府唔封關，社區爆發肯定會發生，呢個時候就要同個政府鬥痴線，睇下邊個頂唔順先。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span>，工會話如果社區爆發發生嘅話就會復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府封關--＞醫護復工<br />\n政府唔封關--＞社區爆發--＞醫護復工<br />\n<br />\n咁我係政府我會唔會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常罷工應該係<br />\n政府唔封關--＞醫院人手不足+社區爆發--＞ 繼續唔復工吹咩--＞部分15 16 嘅醫護頂唔順加入罷工--＞香港淪陷<br />\n<br />\n呢個先係政府驚嘅野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不論工會係咪真係有決心做到香港淪陷，都要令到你嘅對手相信你有決心</span><br />\n<br />\n第二樣野係閉門會議，工會投票唔延長罷工之前，同醫護高層<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">閉門會議</span>，如果我係一個醫護，我點知你傾左d咩，會唔會因為人嘅私心及金錢誘惑傾緊交出繼續罷工嘅名單，我有朋友做醫護因為閉門會議唔敢罷工。過左咁多個月都仲可以開閉門會議，我真係唔知工會係呢8個月學左d咩。"},{"pid":"dc4537ead737191f80273e33e73a560b4f6704e2","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:15:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3f61fef2f4c358d4f8e5e9789d09900f12be64d","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dfea682b7bd2c334ead4457d6c760e9bd7432648","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d8329078b26803250b8067e255e8a47d9a6e345","tid":1881612,"uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"由醫護罷工失敗個一刻開始，我就知道香港再無可能會再（罷工）成功<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1872880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1872880</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3566d7b2c5d29a0bfcf68dbf9ee8ad6efc7fc118","tid":1881612,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"有冇得自組臨時醫院<br />\n只醫某啲人<br />\n<br />\n但物資上同管理上要點做？<br />\n拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2f204bfff0bbfa7412963d64ff0ea549800882","tid":1881612,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9820415a28c79453432b0d5e61a2bedd606eb189","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3566d7b2c5d29a0bfcf68dbf9ee8ad6efc7fc118","tid":1881612,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"有冇得自組臨時醫院<br />\n只醫某啲人<br />\n<br />\n但物資上同管理上要點做？<br />\n拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"好多緊急服務要用最勁嘅儀器，好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f4c3d24678d7458ad032ad5e77bb8a836e8ed2","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10f260bd49c4151de7fb411f8c6670ba18db9f27","tid":1881612,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f17f00aa0799e4c1dbf2060c2420737b2440d256","tid":1881612,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81c7bd26449bf746301ce3b19d8a959194c5834","tid":1881612,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9820415a28c79453432b0d5e61a2bedd606eb189","tid":